def filter_numbers(string):
    return "".join(x for x in string if not x.isdigit())

def filter_numbers(st):
    return "".join(x for x in st if x not in '1234567890')
filter_numbers = lambda s: "".join(x for x in s if not x.isdigit())

def filter_numbers(stg):
    return "".join(x for x in stg if not x.isdecimal())

def filter_numbers(string):
    return "".join(x for x in string if not (48<= ord(x) and ord(x) <= 58))
